OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,FThe bosses of Royal Mail and Ofcom
OL,7,Fwill be called into Parliament to face
OL,8,Fquestions about letter delivery
OL,9,Fdelays, ITV News understands.
OL,11,FThe executives are being hauled in to
OL,12,Fface questions from MPs on the
OL,13,FBusiness and Trade Committee after
OL,14,Fcomplaints that parcels were being
OL,15,Fprioritised over letters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
