OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772121849
OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,FChair of the committee and Labour MP
OL,7,FLiam Byrne said on Thursday: "The
OL,8,FRoyal Mail service is now so poor that
OL,9,Fthe Committee has resolved to call
OL,10,Fexecutives in to account for these
OL,11,Fissues in Parliament, along with Ofcom.
OL,13,F"The Committee is very concerned by
OL,14,Fconsistent and growing reports, and
OL,15,Fnow many direct representations, about
OL,16,Fsignificant failures in Royal Mail's
OL,17,Fletter delivery service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
