OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,FRoyal Mail issued a warning last week
OL,7,Fthat deliveries would be late in more
OL,8,Fthan 100 UK postcodes, blaming staff
OL,9,Fsickness and the weather.
OL,11,FIt listed 38 delivery offices in the
OL,12,FUK, covering over 100 postcodes, that
OL,13,Fwould be most affected by a slower
OL,14,Fservice.
OL,16,FRoyal Mail's parent company was sold
OL,17,Fto EP Group in April last year, which
OL,18,Fis owned by Czech billionaire Daniel
OL,19,FKretinsky.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
