PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772121849
OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,F"EP Group's takeover was approved on a
OL,7,Flegal undertaking that it would
OL,8,Fmaintain the Universal Service
OL,9,FObligation that is the bedrock of the
OL,10,FUK's postal service. But one year in,
OL,11,Feven First Class deliveries are way
OL,12,Foff track," Byrne said.
OL,14,FThe committee had given Royal Mail two
OL,15,Fweeks to respond to the complaints,
OL,16,Fwith a deadline of Monday 2nd March,
OL,17,Fbut has now taken further action by
OL,18,Fbringing the bosses in to face
OL,19,Fquestions.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
