OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,FOfcom is the independent regulator
OL,7,Fresponsible for overseeing Royal Mail.
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FRoyal Mail serves nearly two million
OL,15,Fpostcodes and is required to deliver
OL,16,Fmail six days a week, and aims to
OL,17,Fdeliver both letters and parcels on
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
