OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,FRegulator Ofcom last year gave the go-
OL,7,Fahead for Royal Mail to scrap second-
OL,8,Fclass letter deliveries on Saturdays
OL,9,Fand change the service to every other
OL,10,Fweekday.
OL,12,FIt launched the changes across 35
OL,13,Fdelivery offices as a pilot, but has
OL,14,Fyet to expand this nationwide across
OL,15,Fall 1,200 sites due to failing to
OL,16,Freach an agreement with the staff
OL,17,Funion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
