OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,FIt is in the middle of a month-long
OL,7,Fdispute resolution process with the
OL,8,FCommunication Workers Union over the
OL,9,Fchanges, and Royal Mail insisted last
OL,10,Fweek it needs to "urgently" roll out
OL,11,Fthe new system as it is missing postal
OL,12,Ftargets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
