OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,FA Royal Mail spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Attending the Business and Trade
OL,8,FCommittee will give us the opportunity
OL,9,Fto discuss the work we are doing to
OL,10,Ftransform Royal Mail and the urgent
OL,11,Fneed to implement changes to the
OL,12,FUniversal Service to deliver the
OL,13,Fservices our customers want and ensure
OL,14,Fwe are financially sustainable for the
OL,15,Flong term."
