OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,FIan Strawhorne, Director of
OL,7,FEnforcement at Ofcom, said: "Millions
OL,8,Fof important letters are arriving
OL,9,Flate, and people aren't getting what
OL,10,Fthey pay for when they buy a stamp.
OL,11,FThese persistent failures are
OL,12,Funacceptable, and customers expect and
OL,13,Fdeserve better.
OL,26,@oD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
