OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772121849
OL,3,CRoyal Mail and Ofcom bosses summoned
OL,4,Cto Parliament over delivery delays
OL,6,F"Royal Mail must rebuild consumers'
OL,7,Fconfidence as a matter of urgency. And
OL,8,Fthat means making actual significant
OL,9,Fimprovements, not more empty promises.
OL,10,FWe've told the company to publicly set
OL,11,Fout how it's going to deliver this
OL,12,Fchange, and we expect to start seeing
OL,13,Fmeaningful progress soon. If this
OL,14,Fdoesn't happen, fines are likely to
OL,15,Fcontinue."
OL,17,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,18,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,19,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,20,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
